Re-selling MC Goods

Matthias Fuchs

October 3rd, 2019

Data description

Looking at color popularity by the year of first registration and by model (ColPopPyPm)

I was inspired to run this analysis after reading this article: https://www.whatcar.com/news/what-are-the-best-car-colours-for-resale-value/n18356.

Average holding duration of cars is 5.6 years in Germany (Focus Online, 2012) and around 8.68 years for new cars (DAT Report, 2016)
